    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name>Tachalfo</name></persName> filio <persName>bone memorie
                                <name>Sicheradi</name></persName> vende a domno <persName
                            ref="#people/3305" key="#Bishops">Hieremias</persName> huius sancte
                        Lucane ecclesie humilis <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>, idest una <rs
                            key="#Petiae #Landed_possessions #Hay/fodder">petia de terra mea, quod
                            est prato</rs>, quas abeo in loco ubi dicitur <placeName
                            ref="#places/382"
                            key="#Confinia #Petiae #Landed_possessions #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Mention"
                            >Tumulo, prope Asilatto</placeName>, qui fuit de iura parentorum meorum,
                        et <rs key="#Confinia">est tenente ipse prato uno caput</rs> in <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Mention"><rs key="#Landed_possessions">terra</rs>
                            <persName ref="#people/3306"
                                key="#Confinia #Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Mention"
                                >Ademari</persName></rs>, et alio caput tene in <persName
                            key="#Fountains">fossa</persName>, lato uno tene in <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder">prato</rs> ipsius <rs key="#Mother_churches"
                            >episcopatui</rs> vestro <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/68"
                            key="#Confinia #Hay/fodder #Mother_churches">Sancti Martini</orgName>,
                        et alio lato tene <rs key="#Fiscal_property #Mention">in <rs
                                key="#Hay/fodder">prato</rs>
                            <persName ref="#people/3308"
                                key="#Confinia #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Mention"
                                >Heriprandi</persName></rs>; petia ipsa de prato sicut circumdata
                        est per designatas locas (…). Prezzo: argentum solidos nove in prefinito.
                        Pena in duplum. Verumtamen convenit inter nos, ut sia a quolibet homo ex
                        suprascripta mea venditio pulsati aut districti fueritis, vel si vos exinde
                        alii homines querere volueritis, et vos nobis exinde autores nec defensores
                        nec querere nec dare nolueritis, aut non potueritis, licentiam abeatis asque
                        nostra persona, si vestra fuerit voluntas, exinde causa agendi (…) cum
                        cartula ista vel qualiter iusta legem melius potueritis (…). <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Adalfredus">Adalfridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive la cartula. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Mother_churches #Bishops">Luca</placeName>. </ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Albertus">Alpertus</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Scabini"><name ref="Teufredus"
                            >Teufridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Scabini">scabinus</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Albertus">Alpertus</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Lambertus">Lamperto</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Giselbertus">Gisalpertus</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Sisemundus"
                            >Sisemundo</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Gisbertus">Ghipertus</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Teudebertus">Teupertus</name></persName>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                <p>ChLA, 81, n. 43, pp. 130-133; MDL, 5/2, n. 764, pp. 459-460</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="additional">
                <p>Collavini 1998: 60, 66</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="links">
                <p/>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Sottoscrizioni autografe: Tachalfo/Tacolfo, Alpertus, Teufridi scabinus,
                    Alpertus, Lamperto, Gisalpertus, Petrus, Sisemundo, Ghipertus, Teupertus,
                    Adalfridi notarius (scrittore). Note tergali: del secolo X: <foreign>cartule
                        venditionis de Asilacto</foreign>; dell’XII: <foreign>venditio in Tumulo
                        p(ro)pe Asilatu(m)</foreign>. Attestazione di beni in Asilatto (Bibbone,
                    Livorno) dei fratelli Aldobrandeschi Ademari e Eriprando II, figli di Eriprando
                    I, che possiamo forse presumere di derivazione pubblica.</p>
            </div>
